text: Alice Trevisan (born 2 July 1986) is an Italian rugby union player. She was a member of the Italian Rugby team. She participated at the 2010 Women's Rugby World Cup, 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup qualification, 2017 Women's Rugby World Cup, and 2015 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2015 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2017 Women's Six Nations Championship.
